page.title: 07BIOGRAPHY
page.content: {BIOGRAPHY OF A SCHOOL CHILD My name is{Helen Lavers}. I was born in Redhill Hospital on October the 29th 1972.My parents are Patrick and Mavis Foulger. We live in 28 Coldshott road, Hurst Green, Oxted and I have lived there all my life. My father is a mechanic and my mother works in a shop that sells linen. I have one sister called{Claire}who is 15 years old. I have a pet called{Cecil}and several other pets. I went to{St {Agathas}nursery school then I went to {Hurst Green}first school. I am now at {Holland}middle school and in September 1985 I will go to{Oxted}County. I have a hobbie which is playing the piano.
